{
  "stem": "24466.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know the-- it was a horrible time for us in the ghetto, because already-- and I was always complaining to my-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]-- that it's impossible to live in such bad-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Conditions-- that I will be able-- not be able to fulfill my work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was saying this in German, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always-- when I have a word with him-- what has to be done, what was done, and this all-- so I told him, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have been many, many times telling him about the conditions in which we are living and that I would not be able to really fulfill my work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the other side, I was frightened also, because working, you know, for the frightening, that-- that for-- for saboteurs, as-- that something could happen, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will not be able really to fill out the work for them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Really, many, many times he was quite an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are doing every possible thing to take us out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who-- who do you mean by us?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people, what they were working for the tanneries-- the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jews was waiting for the [NON-ENGLISH] no-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that happened that it's quite possible the Gauleiter was Murer at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gauleiter-- that is the head of the-- of Lithuania, of like a governor-- a governor-- a SR man, of course.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Murer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-U-R-E-R.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were most probably-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --giving him a lot of presents-- [LAUGHS] --maybe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave the OK of taking out the [NON-ENGLISH] from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in-- in-- sorry-- in December '41.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kailis, they called this, the building-- two blocks of flats.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
